    {
        "title": "教师评定职称办理事项工作流程\n",
        "date": "2017-11-13",
        "content": {
            "entry": "<p><span>关于我校教师在评定职称过程中，须在教务处办理相关事项的工作流程，具体如下：</span></p>\n<p>1<span>、人事处下载相关表格；</span></p>\n<p>2<span>、个人工作量查询，请登录教务处主页，点击“工作量查询”</span>http://210.42.144.70/pjcx/login.aspx<span>；</span></p>\n<p><span><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"/picture/article/27/86/52/fcaa75824b9fb1cf6cb3526097c2/defcde98-04d8-4d4c-9938-939a8cee2e75.png\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>3<span>、评教结果，请登录教务系统（师生端）进行查询；</span></p>\n<p><span><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"/picture/article/27/86/52/fcaa75824b9fb1cf6cb3526097c2/0f207cf9-b35c-4c98-81c2-65c02b7ba12e.png\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>4<span>、评教结果的核实请到教务处评估科（</span>4-422<span>），工作量的核实请到教务处教学运行科（</span>4-426<span>），工作人员核实后，请到教务处政策信息（</span>4-412<span>）加盖教务处公章。</span></p>\n"
        }
    },
    {
        "title": "申请补办CET成绩证明、申请CET成绩核查的方法\n",
        "date": "2017-05-27",
        "content": {
            "entry": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\"><strong>一、</strong><span style=\"font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">   </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">申请补办 CET（纸笔考试）成绩证明的方法</span></strong></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">自2014年起，全国大学英语四、六级考试委员会办公室不再受理申请补办 CET（纸笔考试）成绩证明，办理方式调整如下：</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">请考生登录中国教育考试网(<a href=\"http://chaxun.neea.edu.cn/\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; font-size: 10.5pt; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none\">http://www.neea.edu.cn</span></a>)进行网上办理。</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">该申请仅限于2005年（含2005年）以后的考试。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong> </strong></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: -37.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 37.5pt\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">二、<span style=\"font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">   </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">申请 CET 考试成绩核查</span></strong></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">成绩核查内容为分数是否有错加或漏加的情况；评分标准的执行情况不属复查范围。成绩核查申请仍由全国大学英语四、六级考试委员会办公室受理。办理方式如下：</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong> </strong></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">1．申请材料：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">提供 1）学籍所在院校教务处出具的证明（需加盖公章），证明需含：参加考试时间、考试级别、准考证号等内容；2）身份证复印件。  </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"> </div>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">2．受理时间：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">每次考试成绩发布后一个月内（以邮戳时间为准！）。 </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong> </strong></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">3．申请方式：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">全国大学英语四、六级考试委员会办公室不予当面受理。申请者将学籍所在院校教务处出具的证明及身份证复印件以挂号信方式邮寄至全国大学英语四、六级考试委员会办公室。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"> </div>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">4．反馈方式：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">全国大学英语四、六级考试委员会办公室将核查结果以挂号邮寄方式反馈至申请者。 </span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"> </div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">全国大学英语四、六级考试委员会办公室</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">上海邮政信箱30-14</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">上海市 华山路1954号，200030</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">电话：021-52583311</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">传真：021-62932756</span></div>\n<!-- (责任编辑：考务科) -->\n"
        }
    },
    {
        "title": "中南民族大学毕业、学位证明书与肄业证书办理流程\n",
        "date": "2016-09-27",
        "content": {
            "entry": "<p><strong>中南民族大学毕业、学位证明书办理流程</strong></p>\n<p> 受理对象：中南民族大学普通本科毕业生毕业证书、学位证书遗失者</p>\n<p>办理流程：</p>\n<p>1、所在单位或当地派出所开具证书丢失证明或在公开发行的报刊上刊登证书遗失声明。</p>\n<p>2、在中南民族大学教务处主页下载专区下载《中南民族大学毕业、学位证明书及各类 <br>\n证明申请表》并如实填写完整。</p>\n<p>3、到我校档案室（行政楼1楼）复印毕业存根并加盖公章。</p>\n<p>4、将证书丢失证明（或登载证书遗失声明的报刊）、申请表、毕业存根复印件、2寸蓝底 <br>\n近期免冠登记照片2张和身份证复印件于每月15日前交到教务处教学运行科，并同时将与纸质照 <br>\n片相同的电子照片（以姓名+身份证号命名）发至邮箱：2012045@mail.scuec.edu.cn</p>\n<p>5、每月26日后领取人凭身份证领取证书，如遇周末，时间顺延。</p>\n<p>6、根据中南民族大学《2015年服务性收费项目及标准》规定，补办毕业/学位证明书每 <br>\n份收取工本费30元；加急办理每份收取工本费50元。（加急办理从收到材料之日起，一般情况下3天办结）</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>中南民族大学肄业证书办理流程</strong> <br>\n<br>\n受理对象：修满一学年并下文退学的普通本科学生。</p>\n<p>办理流程：</p>\n<p>1、在中南民族大学教务处主页下载专区下载《中南民族大学肄业证书申请表》如实填写 <br>\n完整并经学院签字、盖章。</p>\n<p> 2、将退学红头文件复印件、办完离校手续后的离校通知单复印件、2寸蓝底照片2张、 <br>\n《中南民族大学肄业证书申请表》及身份证复印件交到教务处运行科。</p>\n<p>3、3日后领取人凭身份证领取证书。如遇周末，时间顺延。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>注意事项：</strong> <br>\n<br>\n1、委托他人办理的，除以上所需材料外，被委托人还需持有委托人的委托书及 <br>\n自己的身份证复印件。</p>\n<p>2、寒暑假及国家规定节假日不予以办理。</p>\n<p>3、教务处主页网址：<a href=\"/s/27/t/1536/main.htm\">/s/27/t/1536/main.jspy</a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n联系人：冉老师 <br>\n联系电话：027-67843813</p>\n"
        }
    },
    {
        "title": "教师申请试卷打印网上流程\n",
        "date": "2016-09-12",
        "content": {
            "entry": "<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0pt\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt\">教师申请试卷打印网上流程</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold\">功能简述：</span></strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">1、教师线上进行试卷印制的申请，确定印制明细，进行试卷的跟踪管理，并为后期结算提供依据。</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">2、提供试卷印制申请单的线上打印。</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">3、提供试卷审核表的线上打印。</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0pt\"><strong> </strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold\">教师流程：</span></strong></div>\n<div>\n<p><br>\n<img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"/picture/article/27/51/50/55bb22154570a0d8384891fd34ec/9636a8c9-12e6-403b-a3bc-6ab33f3dd738.png\"></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>具体操作说明详见附件</p>\n<p><img src=\"/control/FCKeditor/editor/images/file/unknow.gif\" alt=\"\"><a id=\"file1\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/picture/article/27/51/50/55bb22154570a0d8384891fd34ec/5fe819f0-4d7b-479b-872d-cad36251ed7b.docx\">附件.docx</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n"
        }
    },
    {
        "title": "湖北省NCRE考试网上报名须知及流程\n",
        "date": "2016-09-12",
        "content": {
            "entry": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">一、报名网站</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 26.25pt; text-indent: -21pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">报名网站地址：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://119.97.236.29/NCRE_EMS/studentlogin.aspx\">http://119.97.236.29/NCRE_EMS/studentlogin.aspx</a><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">二、网报要求</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">．考生首次报考，须注册登录账号。一旦获得账号，以后可以长期使用。如需修改账号密码或个人注册信息，可登录<span lang=\"EN-US\">ETEST</span>通行证（网址：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\"><a href=\"http://passport.etest.net.cn/Register\">http://passport.etest.net.cn/Register</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">）进行管理。务必妥善保存好本人账号及密码，每次账号登录完成操作后，须及时退出，以防泄密带来不必要的损失。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">．每次考试每个考生可报考多个级别科目（最多<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>科，以考点要求为准），但须在同一个考点报考<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>若因考生在不同考点报考造成考试时间冲突而无法正常进行考试的，由考生自行承担责任。但不能重复报考同一科目。同次考试重复报考相同科目的将取消本次考试各科成绩。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">．考生基本信息、报考信息和照片均由考生本人自行填报并核对，<span style=\"color: red\">考生在进行支付考试费操作前须再次核对相关信息是否正确，一旦网上缴费成功，考生即无权再行修改，所造成后果由考生自行承担。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">姓名中有生僻字无法输入的考生，生僻字请用汉语拼音全拼代替。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode: char; text-indent: 28.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">三、网报流程</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100%; mso-cellspacing: 1.5pt; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1184; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0.75pt; padding-top: 0.75pt; padding-left: 0.75pt; padding-right: 0.75pt\">\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">．考生网上填报<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">准备本人<span style=\"color: red\">近期正面免冠半身彩色证件照（规格：浅蓝色背景；成像区大小为<span lang=\"EN-US\">48mm</span>×<span lang=\"EN-US\">36mm<</span>高×宽<span lang=\"EN-US\">></span>，要求上下方向：头部以上空<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/10</span>，头颈部占<span lang=\"EN-US\">7/10</span>，肩身部占<span lang=\"EN-US\">2/10</span>；左右方向：肩身部左右各空<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/10</span>；图像像素最小为<span lang=\"EN-US\">192</span>×<span lang=\"EN-US\">144<</span>高×宽<span lang=\"EN-US\">></span>，图像文件为<span lang=\"EN-US\">.jpg</span>格式，文件大小在<span lang=\"EN-US\">20KB-200KB</span>之间。不得使用生活照！）</span>，在任意一台互联网终端（电脑、<span lang=\"EN-US\">PAD</span>、手机等）均可完成填报操作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">．网上缴费<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 28pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">考生在进行<span style=\"color: red\">支付考试费<strong>操作前</strong>须再次核对相关信息</span>（如：姓名、证件号、证件类型、照片、报考科目等）<strong><span style=\"color: red\">是否正确</span></strong><span style=\"color: red\">，</span>一旦网上缴费成功，考生即无权再行修改。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">．</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">打印准考证<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">考前<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>天考生使用报名账号登录报名网站即可完成该操作。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 宋体; text-align: center\">流程如下图：</span></p>\n            <div><img width=\"937\" height=\"324\" v:shapes=\"组合_x0020_1 椭圆_x0020_5 下箭头_x0020_6 矩形_x0020_7 右箭头_x0020_8 流程图_x003a__x0020_终止_x0020_9 圆角右箭头_x0020_10 矩形_x0020_11 右箭头_x0020_12 圆角矩形_x0020_13 矩形_x0020_16 右箭头_x0020_17 圆角右箭头_x0020_1 圆角矩形_x0020_2 矩形_x0020_3 矩形_x0020_4 矩形_x0020_14 椭圆_x0020_18 圆角矩形_x0020_19 右箭头_x0020_20 右箭头_x0020_21 右箭头_x0020_22 右箭头_x0020_23 右箭头_x0020_24 右箭头_x0020_25 圆角矩形_x0020_26 右箭头_x0020_27 对角圆角矩形_x0020_28 下箭头_x0020_29\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://119.97.236.29/NCRE_EMS/GSFlow.files/image001.png\"></div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n"
