        "title": "非师范专业学生申请教师资格流程\n",
        "date": "2014-09-16",
        "content": {
            "entry": "<p> </p>\n<div align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt\">非师范专业学生申请教师资格流程</span></strong></div>\n<div align=\"center\"><strong> </strong></div>\n<div><strong> </strong></div>\n<p>\n<table style=\"border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none; margin: auto auto auto 14.4pt; border-collapse: collapse; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"height: 70.5pt\">\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 171pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 70.5pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"228\">\n            <div><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">报名参加省教育学、心理学考试，取得合格证书（一般为每年</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">、</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">9</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">月底进行）</span></strong></div>\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: #d4d0c8; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 36.75pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 70.5pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"49\">\n            <div style=\"text-indent: 84.35pt\"><strong> </strong></div>\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 197.25pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 70.5pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"263\">\n            <div align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">报名参加普通话水平测试，取得二级乙等及以上水平的证书（申请教授中文的学生需取得二级甲等及以上水平的证书）</span></strong></div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-indent: 126.5pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 42pt\">↘</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 42pt\">        </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 42pt\">↙</span></strong></div>\n<p>\n<table style=\"border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none; margin: auto auto auto 122.4pt; border-collapse: collapse; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"height: 83.2pt\">\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 171pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 83.2pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"228\">\n            <div style=\"text-indent: 24.1pt\"><strong> </strong></div>\n            <div align=\"center\"><strong> </strong></div>\n            <div align=\"center\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">本校应届</span></u></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">毕业生在毕业的那个学期报名参加面试（即教育教学能力测试）</span></strong></div>\n            <div style=\"text-indent: 126.5pt\"><strong> </strong></div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-indent: 126.5pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 42pt\">  </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 42pt\">↓</span></strong></div>\n<p>\n<table style=\"border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none; margin: auto auto auto 131.4pt; border-collapse: collapse; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr style=\"height: 101.25pt\">\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 135pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 101.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"180\">\n            <div align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">经过审核、考察与测试，由认定机构发给教师资格证书</span></strong></div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n</p>\n<div align=\"left\"><strong> </strong></div>\n<p><!-- (责任编辑：admin) --></p>\n"
